 .../amd/display/dc/dce/dce_stream_encoder.c   | 30 +++++++++----------
 .../display/dc/dce110/dce110_hw_sequencer.c   | 22 +++++++-------
 .../display/dc/dcn10/dcn10_stream_encoder.c   | 30 +++++++++----------
